<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>947</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tiān shàng de fēi niǎo yě bù zhǒng yě bù shōu, yě bù jī xù zài cāng lǐ, yě bù jī xù zài cāng lǐ.
 wǒ men de shén, jiù shì wǒ men de tiān fù, shàng qiě yǎng huó tā, gèng hé kuàng shì nǐ.
 yě de de bǎi hé huā, bù fǎng yě bù zhī, nǐ kàn tā suǒ chuān dài de, bǐ suǒ luō mén hái róng huá.
 suǒ yǐ nǐ bù yào wèi míng tiān yōu lǜ. nǐ de xū yào tiān fù shì zhī dào de.
 zhǐ shì yào xiān qiú tā de guó hé tā de yì, zhè xiē dōng xī dōu yào jiā gěi nǐ, dōu yào jiā gěi nǐ.</lyrics>
<title>bù yào wèi míng tiān yōu lǜ 迦南947</title>
</song>